<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>永旺</title><link>https://aeon.co/feed.atom</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 18:13:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>菌根真菌：陆地生命的根源</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/when-algae-met-fungi-the-hidden-story-of-lifes-most-successful-partnership?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://alpha.aeon.co/images/d05981af-f965-44f6-bedd-c17a2ffe239f/header_mycorrhizal-fungi-the-roots-of-life-on-land-landscape-5.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;埋在土壤中的是一个隐藏的网络，它改变了地球，并在当今的生态系统中发挥着至关重要的作用&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/when-algae-met-fungi-the-hidden-story-of-lifes-most-successful-partnership?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 11:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/when-algae-met-fungi-the-hidden-story-of-lifes-most-successful-partnership?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>语言是良药</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/language-is-at-the-heart-of-indigenous-community-health?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="一名身着传统原住民服装的妇女和两个孩子站在圆锥形帐篷前" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/b684946f-0e98-4b9f-999d-52284b147bd5/header_v1-essay-panos_00252354.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;对于原住民来说，健康不是身体的机械健康问题，而是语言、身份和归属感的问题&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——艾丽卡 X 艾森&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/language-is-at-the-heart-of-indigenous-community-health?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/language-is-at-the-heart-of-indigenous-community-health?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>多诺万</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/why-cleaning-up-crime-scenes-requires-a-rare-mix-of-grit-and-empathy?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://alpha.aeon.co/images/630b52c7-4d91-4551-bc2b-c6ccf46b0c01/header_donovan-landscape-3.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;为了完成一项必要但被忽视的工作，法医清洁工利用了对死者深切关怀和尊重的个人道德&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/why-cleaning-up-crime-scenes-requires-a-rare-mix-of-grit-and-empathy?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 11:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/why-cleaning-up-crime-scenes-requires-a-rare-mix-of-grit-and-empathy?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>伊朗的世俗主义</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/secularism-in-iran-is-not-just-a-form-of-western-imperialism?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="两位穿着现代风格头巾的时尚女性走下蓝天下的台阶" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/f87db89a-8610-44b6-868a-3c78de1a06ab/header_essay-rtsj5ybd.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;后殖民知识分子和伊朗统治者一致认为，世俗主义只是伪装的西方帝国主义。他们错了&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——帕特里克·哈桑和侯赛因·达巴格&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/secularism-in-iran-is-not-just-a-form-of-western-imperialism?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/secularism-in-iran-is-not-just-a-form-of-western-imperialism?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>生病的城市</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/how-the-new-york-of-robert-moses-shaped-my-fathers-health?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/0c7aeab3-0314-40f2-a3b7-14372b2839a6/header_this-essay-cross_bronx_expressway_-_nara_-_549890.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;我父亲在罗伯特·摩西的纽约长大。他的故事证明了城市规划如何塑造无数人的生活&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——凯蒂·穆尔科斯基&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/how-the-new-york-of-robert-moses-shaped-my-fathers-health?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/how-the-new-york-of-robert-moses-shaped-my-fathers-health?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>怎样数一匹狼</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/from-helicopter-flybys-to-trail-cameras-theres-no-one-way-to-count-a-wolf?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/91e87250-47e0-4387-9b19-56908a17adce/header_how-to-count-a-wolf-landscape-5.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;种群数量是保护工作的关键，但统计狼的数量并非易事，这给狼和生物学家都带来了风险&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/from-helicopter-flybys-to-trail-cameras-theres-no-one-way-to-count-a-wolf?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/from-helicopter-flybys-to-trail-cameras-theres-no-one-way-to-count-a-wolf?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>哲学何去何从？</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/since-when-is-philosophy-a-branch-of-the-self-help-industry?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="地下通道上的涂鸦标牌上写着“生命太短暂，不能浪费在追求幸福上”；它反映在下面的池水中" src="https://alpha.aeon.co/images/d8f6d901-b274-4a78-b492-c5136c339081/header_essay-final-gettyimages-1212093725.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;今天，该学科发现自己在难以理解的专业化和廉价的自助之间不稳定地平衡&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——西沃恩·莱昂斯&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/since-when-is-philosophy-a-branch-of-the-self-help-industry?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/since-when-is-philosophy-a-branch-of-the-self-help-industry?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>为什么音乐打动我们</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/an-oceanic-lullaby-gimme-shelter-and-more-elucidate-how-music-taps-into-our-emotions?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img 